{"tid":1448613,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今次革命過後，必須聯手文革式批鬥香港警察","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:57.000Z","uid":277589,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac0938c0c54c02e91c5b76136406b2f421a9cb7","tid":1448613,"uid":277589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:20.000Z","msg":"香港警察，必須清算<br />\n我極討厭文革式批鬥<br />\n但係黑警<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我絕對讚成用文革式批鬥清算</span><br />\n<br />\n批鬥到佢地老逗搵仔咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仔批鬥警老逗<br />\n老逗批鬥警仔<br />\n唔參與批鬥一律比大眾批鬥</span><br />\n黑警必須清算"},{"pid":"bcb4ad30c77233ab1de7fb4417b34d412aa7a285","tid":1448613,"uid":277589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"令佢地係社會得返警察部同事既朋友，服務業一律閪黑警臉，銷售業對黑警無折扣，坐地鐵都要比人屌兩句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">批到佢地懷疑人生</span>"},{"pid":"8161746abc37fa35fbfd767f72222d5a29087d5d","tid":1448613,"uid":241776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=3e298f51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e512621c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"d3df7b9702d6efbc6708595ac8966747a7aed227","tid":1448613,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"贏到咪有得清算囉，輸左等俾人清算啦"},{"pid":"ffece665d7b3996ba78b560f5da16a60fe6ddb61","tid":1448613,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"捉晒入去,比班黑社會打死算啦"},{"pid":"50ebd73b9533cbbbf43fcce63f1eee587d824ad5","tid":1448613,"uid":277589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3df7b9702d6efbc6708595ac8966747a7aed227","tid":1448613,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"贏到咪有得清算囉，輸左等俾人清算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"輸贏都必須清算，日常生活批鬥就足夠<br />\n父母既，就教細路杯葛警察家庭小朋友<br />\n上班族就杯葛有黑警家人既同事"},{"pid":"005ead71d20687e6bceaee2e56c591abfbb8c1b2","tid":1448613,"uid":277589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"必須支持老逗搵仔，係批鬥第一步"}]}